Type: Package
Package: truncpois
Title: Truncated Poisson Distribution
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-05
Authors@R: c(
    person("Arun", "Sundar Paulraj", , "arun.paulraj.2026@mumail.ie", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Keefe", "Murphy", , "keefe.murphy@mu.ie", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides functions for the left-truncated, right-truncated,
    and doubly-truncated Poisson distribution, including density (dtruncpois),
    cumulative distribution function (ptruncpois), quantile function
    (qtruncpois), and random generation (rtruncpois). Also includes
    closed-form functions for the mean (extruncpois), variance
    (vartruncpois), median (medtruncpois), and mode (modtruncpois) of the
    truncated Poisson distribution.
